OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775135469
OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after care home
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FTwo people have been taken to hospital
OL,7,Fand 21 others were treated at the
OL,8,Fscene of a major fire at a care home.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,Fscene at Queen's Promenade in
OL,12,FBlackpool shortly after 8pm on
OL,13,FWednesday, 2 April, Lancashire Police
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe North West Ambulance Service
OL,17,Fdeclared a major incident, which has
OL,18,Fsince been stood down.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
