PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775135469
OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after care home
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FA spokesperson said 21 people were
OL,7,Fassessed at the scene and discharged
OL,8,Fand two people were taken to Blackpool
OL,9,FVictoria Hospital by ambulance to be
OL,10,Ftreated.
OL,12,FLancashire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,13,Fhave confirmed they do not believe the
OL,14,Ffire is suspicious.
OL,16,FFirefighters wore breathing equipment
OL,17,Fand used several hose reels to
OL,18,Fextinguish the fire, authorities said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
