PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775135469
OL,3,CTwo people in hospital after care home
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FThe service confirmed the incident had
OL,7,Fbeen reduced to one fire engine at
OL,8,F10pm and a number of local road
OL,9,Fclosures remained in place.
OL,11,FNorth West Ambulance Service NHS Trust
OL,12,Fconfirmed in a Facebook post that the
OL,13,Fmajor incident had been stood down.
OL,15,F"We dispatched seven ambulances, four
OL,16,FHazardous Area Response Teams, three
OL,17,Fofficers, an advanced paramedic, and a
OL,18,Fdoctor to the scene," they said in a
OL,19,Fstatement.
